00:21:49,635 --> 00:21:53,537
And as much as people say they can look at something early and imagine it, they're really

461
00:21:53,597 --> 00:21:54,377
visual by nature.

462
00:21:54,437 --> 00:21:55,018
Everyone's visual.

463
00:21:56,278 --> 00:21:59,199
And if this image had come out pre-release, then this game would have been a lot less

464
00:21:59,239 --> 00:22:00,540
appealing when people were searching for it.

465
00:22:01,120 --> 00:22:03,901
And of course that went on to be Braid and David's gorgeous art.

466
00:22:05,382 --> 00:22:08,983
So thankfully when you look up Braid online now, you don't see this, you see this.

467
00:22:11,293 --> 00:22:12,936
So that was the first step, making the right game.

468
00:22:13,297 --> 00:22:16,062
And sometimes your champion will find you entirely by themselves,

